°C\/\/speed 0.5<b>."},{"content":"Add cream cheese, rocket and reserved pesto then cook <b>2 min\/100°C\/\/speed <b>."},{"content":"Add prawns and cook <b>2-3 min\/100°C\/\/speed <b> until prawns are pink and cooked thoroughly."},{"content":"Transfer to bowl with pasta and stir gently to combine, adding a little reserved pasta water if necessary. Serve immediately."}],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","55m","4 portions"]}